Insider Activity


Individual




Bruce D. Hansen



Mr. Bruce D. Hansen is on the Board of Directors at ASA Gold & Precious Metals Ltd., Nevada Mining Association, General Moly, Inc. and Energy Fuels, Inc. Mr. Hansen was previously employed as Interim Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Idaho General Mines, Inc., Senior VP-Operations Services & Development by Newmont Mining Corp., Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by Newmont Mining Corp. of Canada Ltd., and Senior Vice President-Corporate Development by Santa Fe Pacific Gold Corp. He received his undergraduate degree from Colorado School of Mines and an MBA from The University of New Mexico.



