About Us We are a group of collectors who focus on products produced by and information about the former A.C. Gilbert Company.
Our goals are to ¶ Showcase and celebrate the works of A.C.Gilbert ¶ Promote the Heritage Society by educating the public and by showing the works of our members.
Website by Dave Gilbert Graphic Design
